Sentencas: The Microstructure of Ni-GDC anode functional layers (AFLs) for lower temperature solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) were investigated.
Titulo: Comprehensive quantification of Ni-Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 anode functional layer microstructures by three-dimensional reconstruction using a FIB/SEM dual beam system

Sentencas: AFLs with various Ni-GDC compositions (50-80 wt% NiO in AFL before reduction) were quantified by a 3D reconstruction technique using a focused ion beam (FIB)/scanning electron microscope (SEM) dual beam system.
Titulo: Comprehensive quantification of Ni-Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 anode functional layer microstructures by three-dimensional reconstruction using a FIB/SEM dual beam system

Sentencas: Each AFL sample was sectioned into 150 slices with 60 nm intervals.
Titulo: Comprehensive quantification of Ni-Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 anode functional layer microstructures by three-dimensional reconstruction using a FIB/SEM dual beam system

Sentencas: Amira software allowed for alignment, segmentation, and reconstruction of the 2D SEM images into a 3D image.
Titulo: Comprehensive quantification of Ni-Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 anode functional layer microstructures by three-dimensional reconstruction using a FIB/SEM dual beam system

Sentencas: From these reconstructions, volume fractions, effective particle size, phase gradient, and surface area for Ni, GDC, and pore phases were quantified.
Titulo: Comprehensive quantification of Ni-Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 anode functional layer microstructures by three-dimensional reconstruction using a FIB/SEM dual beam system

Sentencas: The estimated phase volume fraction was well matched with the theoretical value.

Titulo: Comprehensive quantification of Ni-Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 anode functional layer microstructures by three-dimensional reconstruction using a FIB/SEM dual beam system
